    <node id="&quot;SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC)&quot;">
      <data key="d0">36bf2224-267c-4397-9ff6-b1c0bd5f13eb</data>
      <data key="d1">0</data>
      <data key="d2">"MODULE"</data>
      <data key="d3">"The Serial Data Controller is a hardware module providing an APB slave interface and SPI-compatible serial interface for communication with external devices."</data>
      <data key="d4">['1ebec9d4116bf8cbf50f571b0ab39e17333c538abac0d28b63067bdab402d5970474677a6cee5ae03345e578579b1c858f90bcfd21be21f87c7bb8f66e408a5f']</data>
      <data key="d5">1</data>
      <data key="d6">32</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;APB SLAVE INTERFACE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">ed4b70ab-375f-44c5-b212-1a91befbc795</data>
      <data key="d1">1</data>
      <data key="d2">"INTERFACE"</data>
      <data key="d3">"An APB slave interface allows host processor configuration and communication with external devices."</data>
      <data key="d4">['1ebec9d4116bf8cbf50f571b0ab39e17333c538abac0d28b63067bdab402d5970474677a6cee5ae03345e578579b1c858f90bcfd21be21f87c7bb8f66e408a5f']</data>
      <data key="d5">1</data>
      <data key="d6">16</data>
    </node>
