    <edge source="&quot;SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC)&quot;" target="&quot;APB SLAVE INTERFACE&quot;">
      <data key="d7">2b5c4c93-b9e5-439f-8cf1-b23e0a37d4a7</data>
      <data key="d8">0</data>
      <data key="d9">The SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC) provides an APB SLAVE INTERFACE for communication with the host processor. This interface enables the SDC to facilitate configuration and communication with the host processor, as well as with external devices. Through the APB SLAVE INTERFACE, the SDC allows the host processor to configure and interact with the SDC, and also enables the SDC to communicate with external devices. This functionality is crucial for the SDC's operation, as it relies on the APB SLAVE INTERFACE to exchange data and commands with the host processor and external devices. 

The SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC) and the APB SLAVE INTERFACE work together to enable seamless communication and configuration. The SDC's provision of the APB SLAVE INTERFACE is a key aspect of its design, as it allows for flexibility and ease of use in a variety of applications. By providing a standard interface for communication, the SDC and the APB SLAVE INTERFACE simplify the process of integrating the SDC into larger systems, and enable developers to focus on other aspects of their design. 

In summary, the SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC) and the APB SLAVE INTERFACE are closely related, with the SDC providing the APB SLAVE INTERFACE for communication and configuration. This interface is a critical component of the SDC's functionality, and enables the SDC to interact with the host processor and external devices. By providing a comprehensive and flexible interface, the SDC and the APB SLAVE INTERFACE enable efficient and effective communication, and are essential components in a wide range of applications.</data>
      <data key="d10">18.0</data>
      <data key="d11">48</data>
      <data key="d12">['1ebec9d4116bf8cbf50f571b0ab39e17333c538abac0d28b63067bdab402d5970474677a6cee5ae03345e578579b1c858f90bcfd21be21f87c7bb8f66e408a5f'
 '1ebec9d4116bf8cbf50f571b0ab39e17333c538abac0d28b63067bdab402d5970474677a6cee5ae03345e578579b1c858f90bcfd21be21f87c7bb8f66e408a5f']</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC)&quot;" target="&quot;SPI INTERFACE&quot;">
      <data key="d7">1286101a-211f-4dbb-8e4d-cd51c29ad2c0</data>
      <data key="d8">1</data>
      <data key="d9">The SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC) is a device that enables communication with external slave devices using the SPI INTERFACE. It provides an SPI INTERFACE for communication with these external devices, supporting various features that facilitate efficient data transfer. One of the key features of the SDC is its ability to support configurable baud rates, which allows for flexibility in communication speed. Additionally, the SDC also supports hardware flow control, ensuring that data transmission is managed effectively and reducing the likelihood of errors or data loss.

Through the SPI INTERFACE, the SDC establishes a connection with external slave devices, allowing for the exchange of data between the SDC and these devices. The SPI INTERFACE is a crucial component of the SDC, as it enables the SDC to communicate with external devices and transfer data. The SDC's support for configurable baud rates and hardware flow control makes it a reliable and efficient device for managing communication with external slave devices.

Overall, the SERIAL DATA CONTROLLER (SDC) and its SPI INTERFACE work together to provide a robust and flexible communication system. The SDC's features, including configurable baud rates and hardware flow control, make it an effective device for managing data transfer with external slave devices. By utilizing the SPI INTERFACE, the SDC can communicate with a variety of external devices, making it a versatile and useful device in a range of applications.</data>
      <data key="d10">10.0</data>
      <data key="d11">42</data>
      <data key="d12">['1ebec9d4116bf8cbf50f571b0ab39e17333c538abac0d28b63067bdab402d5970474677a6cee5ae03345e578579b1c858f90bcfd21be21f87c7bb8f66e408a5f'
 '1ebec9d4116bf8cbf50f571b0ab39e17333c538abac0d28b63067bdab402d5970474677a6cee5ae03345e578579b1c858f90bcfd21be21f87c7bb8f66e408a5f']</data>
    </edge>
